history.content:
CS & CS-intended students, see this message from the Office of the Registrar for your deadline to change your grading option this semester:

Dear Student,

The last day to change your grading option for Spring 2019 is 4/5/19 at 11:59:00pm PST in CalCentral > My Academics > Class Enrollment > Change Grading Option.

If you do not plan to change a grading option for your class, you are recommended to verify your current grading options for each class and update them as necessary before the deadline.

If your class has a discussion section, you must choose the same discussion you are enrolled in to proceed with the grading option request.

If you do not see your discussion section, click the right arrow button to navigate through additional pages of discussion sections and choose your current enrolled section.

If you still do not see your discussion section, please contact the department offering the class.

If you are redirected to another page after clicking Change Grading Option - please clear your browser's cache.
